# Improve-ImgSLI

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) and [docs/dev/README.md](../../docs/dev/README.md) before making changes.

Cursor skills (auto-invoked when relevant): `imgsli-devtools`, `sli-ui-toolkit-docs-first` under `.cursor/skills/`.

## Hard rules

- Redux-style store only: `Action → Dispatcher → RootReducer → Store`. EventBus is for past facts, not state.
- Toolkit widgets: painter pipeline; no QSS on toolkit controls; no raw form layouts for construction.
- New workspace tab: `src/tabs/<name>/` with `TabContract` — keep tab logic out of `core/`.
- Canvas / export / video snapshot rendering must stay visually consistent.
- User-visible strings and Help topics update with the feature.

## Tooling

```bash
./launcher.sh context --cloc-only  # code-size stats → cloc.txt (gitignored)
./launcher.sh test tests/contracts # architectural contract tests first
./launcher.sh run --debug          # enables runtime tracer
./launcher.sh run --ui-inspector   # widget / palette / QSS diagnostics
```

Docs: search `docs/dev/` and read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) in-repo — no bundled doc dump.

Runtime tracer: `docs/dev/TRACING.md` (`IMGSLI_TRACE=1`, output `~/.local/share/ImproveImgSLI/trace.jsonl`).

